          <item>
            <title>v1.3.3</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
              <p>My apologies! In a major oversight, I managed to include the usage of a OS X 10.10 only method which appears to be causing crashes on OS X 10.9 and below. This new version contains that fix!</p>

<p>It also contains a new feature, which is a preference that allows you to show the current song’s album art as the dock icon! Many thanks to <a href="https://github.com/matthewlloyd" class="user-mention">@matthewlloyd</a> for that one.</p>

